properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 8 at 3:25AM EST until January 11 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds increasing to 20 to 25 kt beginning tonight,
becoming southeast and gusting to around 30 kt. Seas building
up to 7 to 9 feet.

* WHERE...Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 0-20 nm.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 7 PM EST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 PM THIS EVENING TO 7 PM SATURDAY
